title: Gary Myrick - Scarecrow King
description:
Former New Wave wunderkind Gary Myrick turned in his skinny tie and peg leg jeans for some Texas blues and boogie.

If you like Jeff Healey or Stevie Ray Vaughn, you will totally dig this.
